Organizing the metadata - linking the MiSeq run sample sheet to the Oikonos metadata and then the genotypes.

# read in metadata from Oikonos
meta <- read_csv("../data/metadata/Oikonos_BFAL_Metadata_12.21.2022.csv") %>%
  select(-c(20:27))
